## Typography Hierarchy (2026)

### Font Weights & Sizes

- **Page Headings (H1)**:
  - Size: `text-5xl` (48px)
  - Weight: `font-extrabold`
  - Color: `#1f2937`
  - Use for: Main page titles like "Welcome Back", "Get Started"

- **Page Titles (H1)**:
  - Size: `text-3xl` (30px)
  - Weight: `font-bold`
  - Color: `#111827` (light), `#f1f5f9` (dark)
  - Use for: Main page titles like "Members", "Settings"
  - Subtitle: `text-base`, `#6b7280` (light), `#94a3b8` (dark)

- **Section Headings (H2)**:
  - Size: `text-3xl` (30px)
  - Weight: `font-bold`
  - Color: `#111827` (light), `#f1f5f9` (dark)
  - Use for: Major section breaks

- **Card Titles**:
  - Size: `text-base` (16px) for member/item names
  - Weight: `font-semibold` or `font-bold`
  - Color: `#111827` (light), `#f1f5f9` (dark)
  - Line height: `lineHeight: 22` for better readability
  - Use for: Card headers, member names, item titles

- **Body Text**:
  - Size: `text-base` (16px)
  - Weight: `font-normal`
  - Color: `#6b7280`
  - Line height: `lineHeight: 24`
  - Use for: Descriptions, explanatory text

- **Small Text**:
  - Size: `text-sm` (14px)
  - Weight: `font-medium` or `font-normal`
  - Color: `#6b7280`
  - Line height: `lineHeight: 20`
  - Use for: Helper text, card descriptions

- **Button Text**:
  - Size: `text-sm` (14px)
  - Weight: `font-semibold` or `font-bold`
  - Use for: Primary actions

### Line Height Best Practices

- Body text (base): `lineHeight: 24`
- Small text: `lineHeight: 20`
- Extra small: `lineHeight: 18`
- Headings: Can be tighter but never cramped

## Button & Interactive Elements

### Primary Buttons

- Use the default primary button styling from Gluestack
- Size: `size="lg"` for important actions
- Loading states: Show spinner with `<ButtonSpinner />`
- Text: `font-semibold` or `font-bold`

### Selection Cards (TouchableOpacity + Box)

- Use `TouchableOpacity` with `activeOpacity={0.7}` for press feedback
- Card style:
  ```javascript
  className="rounded-xl" // 12px border radius
  style={{
    backgroundColor: isDark ? '#1e293b' : '#ffffff',
    padding: 16, // p-4
    marginBottom: 10,
    shadowColor: '#000',
    shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
    shadowOpacity: isDark ? 0.3 : 0.06,
    shadowRadius: 8,
    elevation: 3,
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderColor: isDark ? '#334155' : '#f3f4f6',
  }}
  ```
- Internal padding: `p-4` (16px) for member/list cards
- Gap between elements: `gap-3` (12px)
- Include chevron icon on the right if clickable: `#64748b` (light), `#64748b` (dark)

### Link/Text Buttons

- Color: Use primary color `#6366f1`
- Weight: `font-semibold`
- Size: `text-sm`
- Include back arrows in accent colors

### Tab/Segmented Control

- Container: Elevated white card with subtle shadow and border
- Background: `#ffffff` (light), `#1e293b` (dark)
- Border: `borderWidth: 1`, `borderColor: '#f3f4f6'` (light), `'#334155'` (dark)
- Border radius: `rounded-xl` (12px)
- Internal padding: `p-1` (4px gap between tabs)
- Active tab:
  - Background: `#6366f1` (light), `#1e40af` (dark)
  - Text color: `#ffffff`
  - Border radius: `rounded-[10px]` (slightly smaller than container)
  - Padding: `py-3 px-4` (12px vertical, 16px horizontal)
- Inactive tab:
  - Background: `transparent`
  - Text color: `#6b7280` (light), `#94a3b8` (dark)
  - Same padding as active
- Icon size: `18px` for tab icons
- TouchableOpacity: `activeOpacity={0.7}` for press feedback
- Example:
  ```javascript
  <Box className="rounded-xl" style={{
    backgroundColor: isDark ? '#1e293b' : '#ffffff',
    shadowColor: '#000',
    shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
    shadowOpacity: isDark ? 0.3 : 0.06,
    shadowRadius: 8,
    elevation: 3,
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderColor: isDark ? '#334155' : '#f3f4f6',
  }}>
    <HStack className="gap-1 p-1">
      {/* Tab buttons */}
    </HStack>
  </Box>
  ```

### Search Bar

- Container: Elevated white card matching tab switcher style
- Border radius: `rounded-xl` (12px)
- Internal layout: `HStack` with icon, input, and optional clear button
- Padding: `px-4 py-3` (16px horizontal, 12px vertical)
- Icon: Search icon `20px`, color `#9ca3af` (light), `#94a3b8` (dark)
- Input: `flex-1`, `fontSize: 15`, full color for text
- Placeholder: `#9ca3af` (light), `#64748b` (dark)
- Clear button: Close circle icon `20px`, appears when text exists
- Gap between elements: `gap-3` (12px)

### Filter Chips

- Container: `HStack` with `gap-2` and `flexWrap: 'wrap'`
- Chip style:
  - Padding: `py-1.5 px-3` (6px vertical, 12px horizontal)
  - Border radius: `rounded-lg` (8px)
  - Border: `borderWidth: 1`
- Active chip:
  - Background: `#6366f1` (light), `#1e40af` (dark)
  - Border: Same as background
  - Text: `#ffffff`, `fontSize: 12`, `fontWeight: '600'`, `letterSpacing: 0.3`
- Inactive chip:
  - Background: `#f3f4f6` (light), `#1e293b` (dark)
  - Border: `#e5e7eb` (light), `#334155` (dark)
  - Text: `#6b7280` (light), `#94a3b8` (dark)
- TouchableOpacity: `activeOpacity={0.7}`

