## Form Design

### Form Cards

- Wrap form sections in elevated white cards
- Each major section (Personal Info, Church Info) gets its own card
- Card header with icon + title + description
- Internal spacing: `gap-5` between form fields

### Input Fields

- Use Gluestack Input components with `variant="outline"` and `size="lg"`
- Labels: `text-sm font-medium` in `#374151`
- Spacing: `mt-2` between label and input
- Error messages: `mt-1` below input in red

### Form Labels

- Always include labels (no placeholder-only inputs)
- Required fields: Add red asterisk `<Text className="text-error-500"> *</Text>`
- Optional fields: Add "(Optional)" in lighter color below label

## Spacing & Layout (Modern)

### Vertical Spacing

- Between cards: `gap-6` (24px)
- Between form fields: `gap-5` (20px)
- Between tightly related items: `gap-2` or `gap-3`
- Section headers to content: `mb-5` or `mb-6`

### Horizontal Spacing

- Icon to text: `gap-3` or `gap-4`
- Button groups: `gap-3` minimum
- Card internal padding: `p-6` for major cards, `p-4` for smaller ones

### Page Padding

- Standard: `px-6` horizontal (24px)
- Top: `pt-6` for page headers (24px)
- Bottom: `pb-8` for comfortable scrolling space (32px)
- Between sections: `mb-4` (16px) for related sections, `mb-6` (24px) for major breaks

## Animation Guidelines

### Entrance Animations

- Use `FadeIn` and `FadeInDown` from react-native-reanimated
- Stagger delays by 100-200ms for sequential elements
- Duration: 500-600ms for smooth but not slow animations
- Example: First element 100ms delay, second 200ms delay

### Interactive Animations

- TouchableOpacity: `activeOpacity={0.7}` for clear press feedback
- Avoid jarring scale or transform animations on press
- Keep interactions smooth and responsive
- Use `cursor-pointer` class for web compatibility

## Accessibility & Touch Targets

### Touch Target Sizes

- Minimum button height: 44px
- Recommended card padding: `p-5` or `p-6` for easy tapping
- Icon-only buttons: Minimum 40x40px touch area

### Contrast

- Ensure text on backgrounds meets WCAG AA standards
- Body text minimum: 4.5:1 contrast ratio
- Large text minimum: 3:1 contrast ratio

### Focus States

- Ensure keyboard navigation works
- Visible focus indicators for accessibility

## Empty States

- Container: Centered `VStack` with `py-20` (80px vertical padding)
- Icon container:
  - Size: `padding: 20` (80px total with icon)
  - Border radius: `borderRadius: 999` (fully rounded)
  - Background: `#f3f4f6` (light), `#1e293b` (dark)
  - Icon size: `48px`
  - Icon color: `#9ca3af` (light), `#64748b` (dark)
- Title: `text-xl font-bold`, `mb-2`, primary text color
- Description: `text-sm`, `max-w-xs`, secondary text color, centered
- Context-aware: Different messages for "no data" vs "no search results"

## Badges & Status Indicators

- Style: Rounded rectangle (not pill), `borderRadius: 6`
- Padding: `px-2.5 py-1` (10px horizontal, 4px vertical)
- Text: `fontSize: 11`, `fontWeight: '600'`, `letterSpacing: 0.3`
- Colors: Match semantic meaning (green for success, amber for pending, etc.)
- Examples:
  - Role badges: Match role hierarchy colors
  - Status badges: Pending (amber), Accepted (green), Declined (red)

## Don'ts - What to Avoid

❌ **Don't use flat bordered cards** - Use white cards with shadows instead
❌ **Don't use pure white backgrounds** - Use `#fafafa` or similar
❌ **Don't use gray card backgrounds** - White cards on gray page background instead
❌ **Don't use thick borders** - Use subtle shadows for depth
❌ **Don't use plain icon circles** - Add colored backgrounds to icons or use avatar initials
❌ **Don't use small touch targets** - Minimum 44px height for buttons
❌ **Don't use harsh shadows** - Keep shadows subtle (opacity 0.06-0.08)
❌ **Don't overuse colors** - Stick to the defined color system
❌ **Don't crowd elements** - Generous spacing is modern and readable
❌ **Don't use gradient buttons** - Use solid colors with proper contrast
❌ **Don't use circular avatars** - Use rounded squares (12px radius) for modern look
❌ **Don't forget dark mode** - Always provide dark mode color variants

